noContributors.text: There are no contributors in this meeting
noContributors.note: Message displayed when there are no stage publishers in the meeting.

presentation.note: Name description for the screenshare/display participant card.

screenSharing.note: An identifier placed in a participant list item to show that the participant is currently screen-sharing.

otherParticipant.note: Text shown when there is one extra participant in the overflow card.

otherParticipants.note: Text shown when there are multiple extra participants in the overflow card.

enterFullscreen.note: Aria label for full screen button when fullscreen is disabled.

exitFullscreen.note: Aria label for full screen button when fullscreen is enabled.

openSidebar.note: Aria label for a sidebar button when the respective sidebar is closed

closeSidebar.note: Aria label for a sidebar button when the respective sidebar is open

inviteToStage.note: Label for the section used to invite someone to the stage by sharing the meeting URL

onThisStage.note: Label for the publishing participants list sidebar section

viewers.note: Label for the viewer participants list sidebar section

viewerMode.note: Label for the viewer mode header text

incomingVideoTurnedOff.note: Tooltip for the header info pill when audio-only mode is enabled

copy.note: Aria label for button that copies {value}

copiedToClipboard.note: Success notification for copying an item to clipboard

dismissNotification.note: Aria label for dismissing a notification

broadcastIngestEndpoint.note: Label for the ingest endpoint input.

broadcastStreamKey.note: Label for the stream key input.

unknownChatUser.note: Default name given to a chat user with missing name attribute.

chatSaySomething.note: Placeholder text for the chat composer.

chatConnecting.note: Placeholder text for the chat composer while connecting.

chatDisconnected.note: Placeholder text for the chat composer when disconnected.

scrollChatToBottom.note: Aria-label for the button that scrolls chat messages to the bottom.

freeSlotTitle.note: Title for the 'Free up a slot' modal.

freeSlotDescription.text: Choose a participant to free up a slot for your screen-share. Once you start screen-sharing, this participant will stop screen-sharing or become a viewer.
freeSlotDescription.note: Description for freeing up a slot when a screen-share is attempted in a stage that is at capacity

publishingScreen.note: Loading text displayed while attempting to publish a screen-share

yourScreenShareWillEnd.note: Notice displayed when a user will stop screen-sharing to free up a slot

youAreBeingMovedToViewOnly.note: Notice displayed when a user will unpublish to free up a slot

yourScreenShareWillEndCancelled.note: Notice displayed when a user no longer needs to stop screen-sharing to free up a slot

youAreBeingMovedToViewOnlyCancelled.note: Notice displayed when a user no longer needs to stop publishing to free up a slot
